title: Women Holding Hands Light Skin Tone Medium Skin Tone
description: Two women holding hands, with one having light skin tone and the other medium skin tone. Represents friendship, romance, and close relationships between women.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji depicts two women holding hands, rendered with Apple's signature smooth gradients and soft rounded edges, showcasing a light and medium skin tone. Their hands are gracefully intertwined, illuminated by realistic lighting that emphasizes a sense of connection and solidarity. This representation of partnership and unity on Apple devices is perfect for conveying friendship, romance, or mutual support.
